== Births == * [[Ryakuō]] 3rd year / [[興国]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1340]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Mototada|ja|足利基氏|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Mototada|qq=}}, the second son of {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|足利尊氏|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}}, and the first Kamakura Kubō (died [[1367]]). * [[永正]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1511]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiharu|ja|足利義晴|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Yoshiharu|qq=}}, the 12th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died [[1550]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1869]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 16|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kawakami Bēzan|ja|川上眉山|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kawakami Bēzan|qq=}}, a novelist (died [[1908]]).
== Deaths == * [[Kempo (era)|Kempo]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1213]] {{ill|May 24|ja|5月24日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 24|qq=}}) – {{ill|Wada Yoshimori|ja|和田義盛|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wada Yoshimori|qq=}}, a military commander and the first Shitashō-bettō of the Kamakura shogunate (born [[1147]]).
